headline: How Ozempic maker Novo Nordisk fell behind Eli Lilly in the weight loss drug race
summary: Novo Nordisk (NVO) makes Ozempic, the best-known GLP-1 drug out today. And until quite recently, the Danish pharma giant consistently led the pack in new prescriptions, becoming virtually synonymous with a booming weight loss drug market that could hit $139 billion by 2030.
